Resistant: I use this right before a single mob raid that likes to aoe<br>
<br>
Fearless: has worthless for me, not sure when this can be useful<br>
<br>
Evasive: I have defensive, so not sure when I'll ever be using this one.<br>
<br>
Charge: I use this for mobs that con even, I don't really use this for emergency situations.<br>
<br>
